{"timestamp": "2025-12-12 09:49:40.387724", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Whiskers the cat could talk, and he loved to share his whisker‑whispered wisdom with everyone in the town.  \nOne sunny morning, a shy rabbit named Rosie hopped into Whiskers’ garden, her ears drooping.  \n“Why so sad?” asked Whiskers, his voice as soft as a feather.  \nRosie sighed, “I’m afraid to play with the other animals.”  \nWhiskers twitched his tail and said, “Let’s make a game of it! I’ll be the referee, and you’ll be the star.”  \nSoon, the rabbit bounced, the birds chirped, and even the shy squirrel joined in.  \nWhiskers’ gentle words turned fear into giggles, and the whole garden rang with laughter.  \nWhen the sun set, Rosie thanked Whiskers, her heart light as a feather.  \n**Moral:** A kind word can turn a shy heart into a brave one.", "generation_info": {"model": "gpt-oss:20b", "created_at": "2025-12-12T09:49:39.437699424Z", "done": true, "done_reason": "stop", "total_duration": 326548579449, "load_duration": 78650364, "prompt_eval_count": 8192, "prompt_eval_duration": 6881236421, "eval_count": 33438, "eval_duration": 319567674043, "model_name": "gpt-oss:20b"}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8192, "output_tokens": 33438, "total_tokens": 41630}}
